# How to create a side-by-side bar graph divided by year with certain space to the marks of the next month
# https://kb.tableau.com/articles/HowTo/How-to-create-a-side-by-side-bar-graph-divided-by-year-with-certain-space-to-the-marks-of-the-next-month
# Create following calculation [Month]:
MONTH([Order Date])+0.2*(YEAR([Order Date])-{FIXED:AVG(YEAR([Order Date]))})
